  <body>
    <div class="container">
      {{> pagetitle}}
      <br>
      <div style="text-align: left">
        This project uses a couple of APIs:
        <ul>
          <li>
            MapBox API: In order to retrieve the coordinates (latitude and longitude) of any address or city. MapBox is powered by hundreds of data sources, and a distributed global users base of more than half a billion monthly active users.
          </li>
          <li>
            WeatherStack API: In order to retrieve the weather/forecast of the coordinates retrieved from MapBox API. WeatherStack facilitates the instant retrieval of accurate weather information for any location in the world in lightweight JSON format.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
